{"tid":676533,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"吳偉豪《開心速遞》半裸晒肌益網民","createTime":"2018-05-24T12:26:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-26T10:21:15.000Z","uid":3189,"like":24,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"4c4877c3d480f73a36611ebaaf94a5fb57c991b1","tid":676533,"uid":3189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T12:26:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://cdn.modia.com.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/%E5%90%B3%E5%81%89%E8%B1%AA%E5%BD%B1%E7%89%87%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn.modia.com.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F04%2F%25E5%2590%25B3%25E5%2581%2589%25E8%25B1%25AA%25E5%25BD%25B1%25E7%2589%2587%25E6%2588%25AA%25E5%259C%2596.jpg&h=acb23d4e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n吳偉豪(影片截圖)<br />\n<br />\n藝人吳偉豪有着俊朗的外表以及不俗的身材，加上今年才滿20歲夠晒嫩口，成為無綫新晉「小鮮肉」！儘使作為小鮮肉之一，吳偉豪卻沒有什麼機會騷吓Quali，不過到了昨晚(2號)播出的《愛&middot;回家之開心速遞》，短短廿幾分鐘竟出現幾幕他的露肉鏡頭，睇到一班網民流晒口水！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn.modia.com.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/%E5%90%B3%E5%81%89%E8%B1%AA%E5%BD%B1%E7%89%87%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%961.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn.modia.com.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F04%2F%25E5%2590%25B3%25E5%2581%2589%25E8%25B1%25AA%25E5%25BD%25B1%25E7%2589%2587%25E6%2588%25AA%25E5%259C%25961.jpg&h=eb7cb9f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n吳偉豪(影片截圖)<br />\n<br />\n好身材任睇<br />\n劇情講到楊秀惠飾演的「湯圓圓」不小心把吳偉豪飾演的「朱凌凌」弄髒，故楊秀惠帶吳偉豪到畫室換乾淨衣服，期間她發現對方身材原來不俗，直言：「你都幾大隻㗎喎！」她更邀請吳偉豪做人體素描模特兒，正因為這樣吳偉豪的Body就畀大家任睇足足兩分鐘，而吳偉豪雖然身材算瘦，不過除衫後胸肌腹肌齊晒，仲十分結實！之後有一幕吳偉豪更是除淨條Boxer，搞到好兄弟金城安(周嘉洛飾)都忍唔住周身摸，更表示：「平時包到咁實，原來你咁大隻？個腹好硬喎，個胸咁澎湃嘅？」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn.modia.com.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/%E6%A5%8A%E7%A7%80%E6%83%A0%E7%9D%87%E4%B8%AD%E5%90%B3%E5%81%89%E8%B1%AA%E5%89%AFBody%EF%BC%8C%E9%82%80%E8%AB%8B%E4%BD%A2%E5%81%9A%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1%E5%98%85%E6%A8%A1%E7%89%B9%E5%85%92%E5%BD%B1%E7%89%87%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn.modia.com.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F04%2F%25E6%25A5%258A%25E7%25A7%2580%25E6%2583%25A0%25E7%259D%2587%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%2590%25B3%25E5%2581%2589%25E8%25B1%25AA%25E5%2589%25AFBody%25EF%25BC%258C%25E9%2582%2580%25E8%25AB%258B%25E4%25BD%25A2%25E5%2581%259A%25E8%2587%25AA%25E5%25B7%25B1%25E5%2598%2585%25E6%25A8%25A1%25E7%2589%25B9%25E5%2585%2592%25E5%25BD%25B1%25E7%2589%2587%25E6%2588%25AA%25E5%259C%2596.jpg&h=3cf8e30a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n楊秀惠睇中吳偉豪副Body，邀請佢做自己嘅模特兒(影片截圖)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn.modia.com.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/%E5%90%B3%E5%81%89%E8%B1%AA%E6%9C%89%E5%B9%95%E4%BB%B2%E9%99%A4%E6%B7%A8%E6%A2%9DBoxer%E5%BD%B1%E7%89%87%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn.modia.com.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F04%2F%25E5%2590%25B3%25E5%2581%2589%25E8%25B1%25AA%25E6%259C%2589%25E5%25B9%2595%25E4%25BB%25B2%25E9%2599%25A4%25E6%25B7%25A8%25E6%25A2%259DBoxer%25E5%25BD%25B1%25E7%2589%2587%25E6%2588%25AA%25E5%259C%2596.jpg&h=9969efde&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n吳偉豪有幕仲除淨條Boxer(影片截圖)<br />\n<br />\n網民睇到心心眼<br />\n其實唔止安仔，不少網民都驚訝原來吳偉豪禾稈冚珍珠，大讚他身材弗爆的同時更表示睇到心心眼，還直言：「女的歡呼，男的羨慕！」另外有網民卻笑問：「點解一集可以脫咁多？」不過吳偉豪的Body如此養眼，相信一班網民應該唔會厭嘅！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn.modia.com.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/%E6%9C%B1%E5%87%8C%E5%87%8C%E5%89%AF%E5%A5%BDBody%E6%90%9E%E5%88%B0%E5%AE%89%E4%BB%94%E9%83%BD%E5%BF%8D%E5%94%94%E4%BD%8F%E6%91%B8%E5%BD%B1%E7%89%87%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn.modia.com.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F04%2F%25E6%259C%25B1%25E5%2587%258C%25E5%2587%258C%25E5%2589%25AF%25E5%25A5%25BDBody%25E6%2590%259E%25E5%2588%25B0%25E5%25AE%2589%25E4%25BB%2594%25E9%2583%25BD%25E5%25BF%258D%25E5%2594%2594%25E4%25BD%258F%25E6%2591%25B8%25E5%25BD%25B1%25E7%2589%2587%25E6%2588%25AA%25E5%259C%2596.jpg&h=ab6ed7a4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n朱凌凌副好Body搞到安仔都忍唔住摸(影片截圖)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn.modia.com.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/202403_bf5147ec0529dd7d3da8bb1e972509c9-1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn.modia.com.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F04%2F202403_bf5147ec0529dd7d3da8bb1e972509c9-1.png&h=90fdd678&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有網民透露吳偉豪同周嘉洛都曾經喺劇集騷肌(網上圖片)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/02/202939_64f9d426422f51235da71113121ab635.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F02%2F202939_64f9d426422f51235da71113121ab635.png&h=ca5cba38&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/02/202942_b7208759ff24a815f49587e46332a083.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F02%2F202942_b7208759ff24a815f49587e46332a083.png&h=73e1508d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/02/202944_da65c06b4622fb9dafd3b010cdb6c9ba.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F02%2F202944_da65c06b4622fb9dafd3b010cdb6c9ba.png&h=2af562c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/02/202946_d3eb21fe4c4487fd1d8a63fb2c4ecab4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F02%2F202946_d3eb21fe4c4487fd1d8a63fb2c4ecab4.png&h=2995abcc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/02/202955_b1a8cbc385ee4ccf0f9c4e36952727b4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F02%2F202955_b1a8cbc385ee4ccf0f9c4e36952727b4.png&h=650c5490&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/02/202323_b4e2679a2abe839abffdba8615a75515.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F02%2F202323_b4e2679a2abe839abffdba8615a75515.png&h=0e2fdee0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservi